    "The authors also used an Automatic Multiple Choice Question Generator (AMCQG) which have the advantage of making it simple for instructors to design quizzes for aptitude assessments, where evaluation is achieved by administering an online MCQ test (quiz test) and the Maximum Marginal Relevance method is utilized to identify acceptable distractors, and the total accuracy of the relevant statement selection is 98.90%.",
    "Few existing works are discussed in table 4 related to machine learning approach.",
